sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude as Claude Code
    participant DevOrch as dev-orchestrator skill
    participant Recipe as Recipe Runner
    participant YAML as recipe YAML
    participant Agent as Specialized Agent

    User->>Claude: "/dev implement feature X"
    Claude->>DevOrch: classify task
    DevOrch->>DevOrch: detect workstreams
    DevOrch->>Recipe: invoke smart-orchestrator.yaml
    Recipe->>YAML: parse recipe steps
    YAML-->>Recipe: steps with conditions

    loop For each step
        Recipe->>Recipe: evaluate condition
        alt Condition met
            Recipe->>Agent: delegate to agent (architect/builder/tester)
            Agent->>Agent: execute task
            Agent-->>Recipe: result
            Recipe->>Recipe: store result in context
        else Condition not met
            Recipe->>Recipe: skip step
        end
    end

    Recipe-->>DevOrch: all steps complete
    DevOrch->>DevOrch: reflect on goal achievement
    DevOrch-->>Claude: completion summary
    Claude-->>User: task result
